HEADWORD: Cremocarp
<hw>Crem"o*carp</hw> <pr>(kr⟦ecr⟧m"⟦osl⟧*k⟦aum⟧rp ⟦or⟧
kr⟦emac⟧"m⟦osl⟧-)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>kremanny`nai</grk>
